Minor changes (0-3 months)
--------------------------

sep:
  - Amend jgmenu(1) to explain that sep_height only applies to a sep line
    without text
  - jgmenu(1): add sep_markup and sep_halign

columns:
  - support moving left/right between columns
  - deal with menu_width for columns > 1
  - deal with menu_height for columns > 1 (incl dyamic mode)

Deal with ^pipe() that returns error

init:
  - align center
  - remove tint2 code

geometry.c:
  - reivew the below function to see where menu_width is set
    "geo_get_menu_width_from_itemarea_width()"

lx:
  - Add JGMENU_SINGLE_WINDOW
  - check .desktop files are not Unicode in order to avoid segfault
    (Add unit test to prove problem - to include extace.desktop)
  - Sort items when in 'no_dirs' mode

Hide separators when searching

widgets.c:
	- use struct area instead of x,y,w,h
	- parse align
	- add 'text'

Investigate duplicate .desktop entries on Raspberry Pi and nixOS

jgmenu - warn if strange command line argument is given

modules:
  - dmenu (based on isprog.c)
  - emoji

^rootmenu()

jgmenu-convert.c

